<div class="mainbar">
  <h1>Coding Style</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>Use soft-tabs with a two space indent. Never mix spaces and tabs for indentation.</li>
    <li>Use only classes and tags as CSS selectors and no ids</li>
    <li>Use dashes between words in class name <code>.info-block</code> instead of <code>.info_block</code> or infoBlock</li>
    <li>Use lowercase and shorthand hex values #aaa, unless using <code>rgba(0, 0, 0, .2)</code></li>
    <li>Use single or double quotes consistently. Preference is for double quotes content: ""</li>
    <li>Quote attribute values in selectors <code>input[type="text"]</code></li>
    <li>Separate each ruleset by a blank line</li>
  </ul>
</div>